{
  "stem": "210.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My cousin was no longer in the ghetto, they already sent her out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he was engaged to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So since-- from that time on, he was really wonderful to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He Saved my life I don't know how many times over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He gave me a job, and he had like a-- he lived in, in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was like a suburb of Lodz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was-- and I got a job there in his factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they made straw, straw mattresses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I worked at that time over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he-- you know, this was his-- he was the chief-- the chief over this factor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I worked there, and he was really, very nice to all of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, this lasted for a while.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and then this factory was closed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we worked, like, in a field where they already took out all the potatoes, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just to pick-- put together the potato that were left over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you know, we did that, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had to put it in sacks and put it on one side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when this-- this was finished, and again, I had nothing to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he had-- he had this office.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was like, the-- at that time, I didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But he was like, very high ranking in the Jewish police in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he took me to his work in his office.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I was like, in debt, was-- how do you say that in, in English?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Where they cut trees?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[POLISH] in Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know how they say in English, like a lumberyard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I worked in the-- and he took me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this was like in the middle of the city, and he took me to work in this lumberyard.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
